  <Docs>
    <summary>Provides a Cryptography Next Generation (CNG) implementation of the Module-Lattice-Based Digital Signature Algorithm (ML-DSA).</summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>This algorithm is specified by FIPS-204.</para>
      <para>Developers are encouraged to program against the <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.MLDsa" /> base class rather than any specific derived class.</para>
      <para>The derived classes are intended for interop with the underlying system cryptographic libraries.</para>
    </remarks>
  </Docs>
